aped by viral fads, polarized deb ate, and per formativ e agr eement, the brav ery to question the cr owd is both uncommon and\nnecessar y. Real pr ogress gr ows not fr om aut omatic loyalty t o majority norms, but fr om critical pr obing and the ner ve to challenge what feels\ncomfor table.",
